value.value: A drug-induced hearing loss characterized by hearing loss induced by therapeutic doses of aminoglycoside antibiotics that has_material_basis_in mutation in the mitochondrial genes MTRNR1 or MTCO1 in combination with homozygous mutation in TRMU on chromosome 22q13.31.
